  {
    "content_id": 419456,
    "reference_id": 109055,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "1 Petro 5:1–5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60005001-60005005",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Petro alielezea <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108118\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">wazee wa kanisa</span> na viongozi kama <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108278\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">wachungaji</span> wa watu wa Mungu.</p><p>Maagizo yake kwao yalikuwa kama maagizo ya Yesu kwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108040\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">wanafunzi</span> wake kama ilivyoandikwa katika Luka 22:24–30.</p><p>Viongozi wa kanisa hawapaswi kuwa na kiburi au kujifanya watawala. Yesu ndiye Mchungaji Mkuu na wanapaswa kumtii.</p><p>Lazima wafuate mfano wa Yesu wa kuwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108059\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">kiongozi aliyehudumu</span>.</p><p>Viongozi wanaohudumu kwa uaminifu watashiriki utukufu wa Yesu atakaporudi duniani.</p><p>Waumini wengine lazima waheshimu na kufuata viongozi wanaoongoza kama Yesu.</p>",
