  {
    "content_id": 419457,
    "reference_id": 109056,
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "title": "1 Petro 5:6–14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "60005006-60005014",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Petro alimaliza barua yake kwa kuwatia moyo waumini kwa njia kadhaa. Aliwakumbusha kwamba Mungu anawajali watu wake kwa kweli. Wanaweza kumwamini Mungu kabisa.</p><p>Shetani hujaribu kuwafanya waumini wamtie Mungu shaka na kuacha kumtii. Petro alielezea hili kama shetani kujaribu kuwameza. Lakini Mungu huwapa waumini neema wanayohitaji kumpinga shetani. Wao ni wanyenyekevu lakini Mungu ni mwenye nguvu. Anawapa nguvu kushikilia kile wanachoamini.</p><p>Waumini hawako peke yao wanapojitahidi na kuteseka. Watu wa Mungu kote ulimwenguni pia wanateseka na wanapambana dhidi ya uovu. Wameunganishwa pamoja kama mmoja katika <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108045\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">familia ya Mungu</span> na katika urafiki.</p><p>Salamu kutoka kwa <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108121\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Sila</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108069\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Marko</span> na kanisa pia liliwatia moyo waumini. Petro alitumia jina <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"108498\" data-resourceType=\"BiblicaStudyNotesKeyTerms\">Babeli</span> kuzungumzia Roma.</p>",
